{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SnowplowTracker\/documentation\/SnowplowTracker","doc:\/\/SnowplowTracker\/documentation\/SnowplowTracker\/Snowplow"]]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Reconfigure, create or delete the trackers based on the configuration downloaded remotely."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"refresh"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"onSuccess"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" (["},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":"]?, "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConfigurationState","identifier":"doc:\/\/SnowplowTracker\/documentation\/SnowplowTracker\/ConfigurationState","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@SnowplowTracker@E@SPConfigurationState"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The callback called when a configuration (cached or downloaded) is set It passes the list of the namespaces associated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to the created trackers."}]}],"name":"onSuccess"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The trackers configuration is automatically download from the endpoint indicated in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RemoteConfiguration"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"previously used to setup the trackers."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The method is asynchronous and you can receive the list of the created trackers in the callbacks once the trackers are created."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The downloaded configuration updates the cached one only if the configuration version is greater than the cached one."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Otherwise the cached one is kept and the callback is not called."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"IMPORTANT: The EventStore will persist all the events that have been tracked but not yet sent.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Those events are attached to the namespace.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If the tracker is removed or the app relaunched with a different namespace, those events can’t","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"be sent to the collector and they remain in a zombie state inside the EventStore.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"To remove all the zombie events you can call an internal method ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"removeUnsentEventsExceptForNamespaces"},{"text":" on ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SPSQLEventStore"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"which will delete all the EventStores instanced with namespaces not listed in the passed list.","type":"text"}]}]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Type Method","modules":[{"name":"SnowplowTracker"}],"externalID":"c:@M@SnowplowTracker@objc(cs)SPSnowplow(cm)refreshOnSuccess:","title":"refresh(onSuccess:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"refresh"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"onSuccess"},{"kind":"text","text":": (["},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String"